data.text: HIGH SCHOOL: 2010 graduate of Killeen Ellison High School in Killeen ... Graduated in top 25 percent of class ... Lettered three years in track, coached by Bill Farley ... Recorded personal best times of 10.39 in the 100 and 20.9 in the 200 ... Earned team sprinter of the year honors for highest point total ... Won district 100 title as a senior, but did not compete at regionals ... As a junior placed second in district 100 and third at region meet ... In 2008, as a sophomore, placed second in district 100 and ninth in region ... Teamed with current Aggie Prezel Hardy in winning State 5A 4 x 200 title in 2009 (1:25.66) and finishing as runner-up in 4 x 100 ... Killeen Ellison placed second at State in team scoring in 2009. PERSONAL: Michael Giovanni Bryan is the son of Chris Bryan and Barbara Tyler ... Born June 9, 1991 in Fort Campbell, Tennessee ... Has one sibling, Chris ... Kinesiology major ... Began competing at age 12.
